  "title": "NASCON Maintains Topline Expansion In 2023 Third Quarter Earnings",
  "description": "NASCON Allied Industries Plc (NASCON) published its unaudited financials for the third quarter ended September 30, 2023, in which the company reported a standalone EPS of N1.96 against N0.51 in 2022. ",
  "publishedAt": "2023-11-13T17:15:18+01:00",
  "featuredImage": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dw7w2at8k/image/upload/v1772448792/financialedge/nascon_logo.png",
  "sourceUrl": "https://financialedge.com.ng/nascon-maintains-topline-expansion-in-2023-third-quarter-earnings/",
  "section": "Capital Market",
  "sectionSlug": "capital-market",
  "html": "<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">NASCON Allied Industries Plc (NASCON) published its unaudited financials for the third quarter ended September 30, 2023, in which the company reported a standalone EPS of N1.96 against N0.51 in 2022.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">This brings the nine months  EPS to N4.15 compared to N1.09 that was recorded in the same period in 2022, The EPS increase was driven by the sturdy growth in sales, which stood at  35.3% recorded in the reporting period.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">NASCON’s board has proposed an interim dividend of N1.00/s, while revenue grew by 35.3%, driven by aggressive volume drive in its core geographical area of operations, the Northern region.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">As such, revenue from the North grew by 36.5%, contributing 72.0% of the total sales outturn. In the same vein, revenue from the Western was up by 33.9%  and Eastern was up by 27.2%  regions maintained the momentum witnessed so far in 2023.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">Sequentially, revenue declined by 1.5% quarter by quarter on a broad-based decline across the business’ regions East (-5.5% q/q), North (-1.6% q/q) and West (-0.1% q/q). Gross margin for the quarter increased by 17.95 to 63.8%, buoyed by the aforementioned expansion in revenue and a 9.5% decline in cost of sales.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">The lower cost was driven by a 14.3% decline in raw materials consumed. Consequently, EBITDA  22.99 ppts and EBIT (+24.01 ppts y/y) margins increased markedly to 40.7% and 37.7%, respectively, even as operating expenses increased by 32.3% y/y.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">Further down, NASCON’s net finance cost grew by 69.8% y/y, underpinned by a 56.3% y/y increase in finance cost due to higher interest on borrowings (+190.3% y/y). Meanwhile, finance income grew by 41.3% y/y.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">Overall, profit before tax grew by 285.1% y/y to NGN7.68 billion (Q3-22: N2.00 billion). Following an effective tax rate of 32.5%, profit after tax printed N5.19 billion against N1.35 billion in 2022, translating to a growth of 285.1%.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\">NASCON sustained its impressive performance from the start of the year, following its impressive sales performance and efficient cost management. Considering the resilience witnessed in 2023, its expected that the company will finish the year positively, maintaining robust expansions in its top and bottom lines.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"yiv6421892626msonormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white; outline: none !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'New','serif'; color: #1d2228;\"> </span></span></p>\n"
}